title: 1 BR Apt for rent - Put Prop - 2100 Aldrich Ave #104 - 9/1
posting_body: ['2100 Aldrich Ave S - 1 Bedroom - $1025 - Sept 1st - PET FRIENDLY!!', 'This well maintained property has a terrific 1st floor unit available for "End of August" Move in!!', 'Building is close to Wedge Coop, coffee shops, bus lines to U of MN and Downtown.', 'Walk to Lake of the Isles, Walker and Loring Park!', 'Easy access to I94 and More!', 'Rent includes heat, water, trash and storage closet in laundry room.', 'You only pay electricity and internet.', 'US Internet is available in building, high speed fiber!', 'Updated unit has approximately 650 sq feet, carpeted and ceramic tiled flooring, large closets in entry and bedroom, plus updated kitchen and bathroom.', 'Laundry room remodeled and includes huge storage closets for each unit.', 'Off street reserved parking $70 per month.', 'PET FRIENDLY!!', 'Dogs 50lbs pounds and smaller ok, and cats ok.', 'Limit two pets.', 'A one time pet fee of $300 required plus $35 per month pet rent.', 'Online resident portal available for rent payment and Maintenance requests.', '24 Hour maintenance available.', 'Smoke Free Building!', 'Check out our reviews!', 'Call today to set up a showing!!', 'Nancy', 'show contact info', 'nancy @ putnamproperties .', 'net', 'Or visit us online:', '<URL>', 'Please visit <URL> for more information', '<URL>', 'Sending a message via email (without explicit reply) does not mean an appointment for a showing has been scheduled.', 'Call to confirm an appointment for a showing.']
